<title>
A/C Switch Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
Check A/C switch for terminal-to-terminal continuity. If check result is not as specified, replace HVAC control unit.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
To perform measurement with A/C switch to “ON”, use diode range of circuit tester.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
